items.badge_description: Originating from Germany, the Altbier, or old beer, uses the old school brewing style of top fermentation and is left to condition for longer than normal. That's 5 different beers with the style of Altbier. Try 5 for more Level 2!

items.checkin_comment: Very cool. A nice twist on their classic altbier. A bit sweeter, but more nutty and dried fruit character.
Smells great but way too much vanilla to drink. Apricot doesn't mesh well either. Too bad.

items.checkin_comment: A little sweet for my tastes, but very good nonetheless.  A good dessert beer!!
Some nice honey and malt in there but not spotting the vanilla or apricot
